人冇到所以唔鬼Contribute<br />\n<br />\n成日咁撚得閒上嚟連登出埋啲低質素Post鳩噏問人指教<br />\n不如用啲時間去進修下 醫下你個死人腦好過啦<br />\n<br />\n最後補多次<br />\nfernando我屌你老母"},{"pid":"a1e69f09da3660edc33e966e262213917ab88562","tid":2219341,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T00:48:49.000Z","msg":"on9先做飲食"},{"pid":"700d228e7a444976be8385f9b68354b353ebe95b","tid":2219341,"uid":357199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9446b969d109d35d21c6a60176a33c9e255dece","tid":2219341,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"有排分手期間返水吧， 每日都嬲爆爆 每杯凍檸茶我都一定會吐口水落去， 因為條八婆最鍾意飲凍檸茶 死八婆 害到人地要飲加料野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好搞我杯凍檸茶"},{"pid":"73a904abe7f1c6b2c94ed0659ba351a4d08eb1a2","tid":2219341,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a1e69f09da3660edc33e966e262213917ab88562","tid":2219341,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T00:48:49.000Z","msg":"on9先做飲食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"有咩行好做？"},{"pid":"03bdfa3b3745d356966fe5b7478c9131d1b110b2","tid":2219341,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73a904abe7f1c6b2c94ed0659ba351a4d08eb1a2","tid":2219341,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a1e69f09da3660edc33e966e262213917ab88562","tid":2219341,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T00:48:49.000Z","msg":"on9先做飲食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"有咩行好做？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"學屈sir做實Q"},{"pid":"ca777a0d2201f9011065bc05d8b179be7089baee","tid":2219341,"uid":5674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a2117ec2c112c71b3bae41e26aea9b78e8bba65","tid":2219341,"uid":363651,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T22:39:16.000Z","msg":"做茶記，個阿婆問紅豆冰可唔可以走冰"},"cite